Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 学会了开这玩意儿\N{\fs38}Learning to fly this thing, Morty,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.60,0:00:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后就轻松啦\N{\fs38}Is gonna be really liberating.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.02,0:00:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就可以随便\N{\fs38}You know, you're gonna be free
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 去帮我跑各种活儿了 - 酷\N{\fs38}- To go on all kinds of errands for me. - Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.52,0:00:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见那颗行星了吗\N{\fs38}See that planet right there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.48,0:00:09.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千万别靠太近\N{\fs38}Don't fly too close to that planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.04,0:00:11.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会有人想出来擦你的玻璃窗\N{\fs38}Someone will come out and try to wash your windshld.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.76,0:00:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍等\N{\fs38}Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.64,0:00:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我身上呢 \N{\fs38}Yeah? Yeah, I have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想在哪儿见面\N{\fs38}Where do you want to meet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.36,0:00:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs38}All right, cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 教学结束了\N{\fs38}All right, Morty, lesson's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:21.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点事要处理\N{\fs38}We got some business to attend to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.34,0:00:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这儿往南几光分\N{\fs38}A few light minutes south of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在太空里还用南边这个说法啊\N{\fs38}Oh, you still use south in space?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.34,0:00:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 Jerry \N{\fs38}Whoa! Jesus, Jerry!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.84,0:00:26.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这儿干什么\N{\fs38}What the hell are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.98,0:00:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs38}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们说好了 如果我儿子要学驾驶\N{\fs38}We agreed a boy's father should be present
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:32.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 爸爸我必须在场 - 好像是说过\N{\fs38}- When he's learning to drive. - I guess I remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.36,0:00:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你莫非一直都在后座上\N{\fs38}Wow. And you've just been back there this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.58,0:00:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是神了\N{\fs38}Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没时间把他送回地球了\N{\fs38}Well, we don't have time to take him to earth, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.96,0:00:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去3924917\N{\fs38}Head for 3924917.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.80,0:00:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,酷\N{\fs38}Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.96,0:00:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我也要跟你们一起来冒险啦\N{\fs38}Looks like I'm coming along for an adventure!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.00,0:00:44.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯哼\N{\fs38}Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就是要来这儿吗\N{\fs38}This is where we're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.70,0:00:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs38}Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:50.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这儿才是\N{\fs38}This is.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.56,0:00:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以停在残障专用车位 Morty\N{\fs38}You can park in a handicap spot, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八条腿以下的生物\N{\fs38}Anything with less than eight limbs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.64,0:00:55.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里都算残疾\N{\fs38}Is considered disabled here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.38,0:01:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这个小伙子 长得多俊啊\N{\fs38}Well, look at this fella. Aren't you handsome?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.12,0:01:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢夸奖 \N{\fs38}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.82,0:01:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我是Jerry - 我知道\N{\fs38}- I'm Jerry. - Oh, I know you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.80,0:01:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是不是坐宇宙飞船来的\N{\fs38}Did you come here in a spaceship?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:11.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和儿子岳父一起来的\N{\fs38}I'm traveling with my son and father-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.04,0:01:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 他们不过来吗\N{\fs38}W-wait. Are they coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.58,0:01:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们马上就会回来的\N{\fs38}Oh, they'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.16,0:01:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥\N{\fs38}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个怎么弄\N{\fs38}I don't know how this works!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.78,0:01:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁来帮帮我\N{\fs38}Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么鬼东西\N{\fs38}What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可理喻 是吧\N{\fs38}I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.74,0:01:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么鬼东西\N{\fs38}Oh, what the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.34,0:01:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可理喻 对吧\N{\fs38}I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry保育\N{\fs38}Jerryboree!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.26,0:01:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我爸建了一个日托所\N{\fs38}You created a day care for my dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.20,0:01:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒希望这点子是我想出来的\N{\fs38}Are you kidding? I wish I had this idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.20,0:01:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该说 我确实想到过\N{\fs38}Well, I did have this idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我希望我是握有产权的那个我\N{\fs38}But I wish I was the version of me that owned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.68,0:01:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丫可算是发家了\N{\fs38}That guy's rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得确认托管的原因\N{\fs38}Don't forget to check the reason for your drop-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.60,0:01:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我 别的Rick告诉过我\N{\fs38}Trust me, Morty, I've heard stories from other ricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:45.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry离了地球 五分钟也活不下去\N{\fs38}Jerrys don't tend to last five minutes off of earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是一个完全未注册的时间枢纽小行星\N{\fs38}This is a totally unregistered cross-temporal asteroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以和其他Jerry一起玩耍嬉戏\N{\fs38}Here, they can romp and play with other Jerrys.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.48,0:01:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再安全不过了\N{\fs38}He couldn't be safer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这个收好了\N{\fs38}Hey, Morty, hang on to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面有你爸的编号\N{\fs38}That number's your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.94,0:01:55.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是丢了 他就领不回来了\N{\fs38}If you lose it, we're not gonna be able to get him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:38.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 在这儿等着 - 我也想去\N{\fs38}- Okay, wait here. - I want to come with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.66,0:02:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去什么去 很无聊的\N{\fs38}Don't come with. It's boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:41.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去谈生意\N{\fs38}It's it's business stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在车库里谈什么生意\N{\fs38}What kind of business do you do in a garage?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟见不得人似的\N{\fs38}You know, this seems a little shady.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 你以为见不得人的事情\N{\fs38}Right, yeah, like nothing shady ever happened
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.42,0:02:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富丽堂皇的办公室里就没有了吗\N{\fs38}In a fully furnished office?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说过华尔街吗\N{\fs38}You ever hear about wall street, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.20,0:02:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知不知道这些人\N{\fs38}Y-you know what those guys do
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在高档会议室里干什么勾当\N{\fs38}In, in, in, their fancy boardrooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把蛋蛋放进可卡因里\N{\fs38}They take their balls and they dip them in cocaine
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后互相蹭过来搅过去\N{\fs38}And wipe them all over each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:02:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公我行走江湖\N{\fs38}You know, grandpa goes around,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.28,0:02:58.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做生意都是在大庭广众之下\N{\fs38}And he does his business in public,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.80,0:03:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外公没有什么见不得人的\N{\fs38}Because grandpa isn't shady.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\fs38}Aw, crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.06,0:03:02.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 \N{\fs38}Hey, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.70,0:03:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 Rick\N{\fs38}Hey, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 拿着 三千F币\N{\fs38}Here you go. 3,000 flerbos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器带来了吧\N{\fs38}Do you have the weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们能不能稍微\N{\fs38}C-can we please?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我外孙 Morty\N{\fs38}This is my grandson, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:12.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 Morty 我是Krombopulos Michael\N{\fs38}Oh, hi, Morty. I'm Krombopulos Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个杀手 我从你外公这儿买枪械\N{\fs38}I'm an assassin. I buy guns from your grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你 你快滚\N{\fs38}Here. Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来杀伤力很大嘛\N{\fs38}Ooh! Yeah, this looks deadly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这枪射出的是反物质对吧\N{\fs38}So, this shoots antimatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:21.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的目标用普通物质可是杀不死的\N{\fs38}My target can't be killed with regular matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.18,0:03:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你 Morty\N{\fs38}Nice to meet you, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:24.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想弄死任何人\N{\fs38}Listen, if you ever need anybody murdered,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.12,0:03:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必联系我\N{\fs38}Please give me a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 我从不出岔子 - 你就这么把名片给他了\N{\fs38}- I'm very discreet. - You're g-giving him a card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我干活没有任何道德标准\N{\fs38}I have no code of ethics.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.34,0:03:29.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么地点 什么人都可以\N{\fs38}I will kill anyone, anywhere
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:32.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儿童 动物 老人 都无所谓\N{\fs38}Children, animals, old people. Doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.48,0:03:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀生就是我的爱好\N{\fs38}I just love killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.60,0:03:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你卖武器给杀手来赚钱\N{\fs38}You sell weapons to killers for money?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 你这种思维 就是我们星系间\N{\fs38}You've got what the intergalactic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.84,0:03:39.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所说的典型的拘于世俗\N{\fs38}call a very planetary mind-set, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些事情比你想的复杂得多\N{\fs38}It's more complicated out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.36,0:03:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些可是F币\N{\fs38}These are flerbos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知不知道两个人类有了\N{\fs38}Do you understand what two humans can accomplish
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.90,0:03:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这三千F币能干什么 - 什么\N{\fs38}- With 3,000 of these? - Uh, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在闪电芯疯狂一下午\N{\fs38}An entire afternoon at blips and chitz!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.87,0:03:53.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这地方最棒了\N{\fs38}Oh, this place is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有啤酒 游戏 奖品\N{\fs38}It's got beer, games, prizes,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一玩起来就不知天日\N{\fs38}And you can never tell what time it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把枪卖给杀手就为了玩游戏\N{\fs38}You sold a gun to a murderer so you could play video games?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是成天就想着怎么玩弄文字\N{\fs38}Yeah, sure, I mean, if you spend all day shuffling words around,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事儿都能被你说得这么难听\N{\fs38}You can make anything sound bad, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试试这个\N{\fs38}Here, check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.36,0:04:08.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊\N{\fs38}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Roy 怎么了\N{\fs38}Roy, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了个噩梦\N{\fs38}I had a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟一个老头在一起\N{\fs38}I was with an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.88,0:04:15.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把一头盔戴在了我头上\N{\fs38}He put a helmet on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.42,0:04:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你烧糊涂了 好好休息吧\N{\fs38}It's just a fever. Get some sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想让你周一落下课\N{\fs38}I don't want you missing school on monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你们审视今日\N{\fs38}I want you kids to look around you today
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.16,0:04:25.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后展望未来\N{\fs38}And think about your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.98,0:04:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个年纪 你们的人生充满了可能性\N{\fs38}Now is the time in your life when anything is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个球传得太完美了\N{\fs38}Spiraling perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.88,0:04:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Roy Pasons拿到了球\N{\fs38}It's gonna be caught by Roy Parsons!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.50,0:04:32.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Roy Parsons过了二十码线\N{\fs38}Roy Parsons is at the 20!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:33.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过了十码线\N{\fs38}Now he's at the 10!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.76,0:04:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火箭Roy所向披靡\N{\fs38}Nothing can stop Roy "The rocket"!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:37.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,触地得分\N{\fs38}Touchdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是觉得是时候活得现实一些了\N{\fs38}I just think it's time to get realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和我爸谈过地毯店的事了吗 \N{\fs38}Have you talked to my father about the carpet store?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.72,0:04:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Roy\N{\fs38}Roy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是早点发现就好了\N{\fs38}Had we caught it sooner well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过现在说什么都是马后炮\N{\fs38}Had we caught it sooner well, hindsight is 20/20, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.60,0:04:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是我们要抓紧治疗\N{\fs38}What's important is that we move quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还不想死\N{\fs38}I'm not ready to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.70,0:04:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会死的\N{\fs38}You're not going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:02.62,slogan,,0,0,0,,{\pos(686,205)}火箭不会输给癌症
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Roy 地毯很好 谢谢啦\N{\fs38}Hey, thanks for the carpet, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.50,0:05:10.41,daddy,,0,0,0,,{\fscx108\fscy100\frz2.531\pos(990,968}世界上最伟大的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Roy 你把那些清仓甩卖的波斯白粗毛毯\N{\fs38}Hey, Roy, you pulled those persian off-white shags
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿出来了吗\N{\fs38}for the clearance sale?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.82,0:05:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 妈的\N{\fs38}Whoa. Sh shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs38}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.94,0:05:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 怎么回事\N{\fs38}Whoa! What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.20,0:05:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在哪儿\N{\fs38}W-w-where am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.24,0:05:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 到底怎么回事  - 55年 不错嘛 Morty\N{\fs38}- What in the hell?! - 55 years. Not bad, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然三十多岁的时候\N{\fs38}You kind of wasted your 30s, though,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点把时间浪费在观鸟上了\N{\fs38}with that whole bird-watching phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我老婆呢\N{\fs38}W-where's my wife?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 你刚刚只是在玩游戏\N{\fs38}Morty, you were just playing a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.54,0:05:31.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这游戏就叫"Roy"\N{\fs38}It's called "Roy."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.34,0:05:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快清醒点\N{\fs38}Snap out of it. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是Morty 你是Rick\N{\fs38}I'm Morty. You're Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 你卖了把枪给一个杀手\N{\fs38}Hey! You sold a gun to a guy that kills people!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:37.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,癌症你都熬过来了\N{\fs38}Look at this, you beat cancer,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然又回到那个地毯店上班\N{\fs38}and then you went back to work at the carpet store?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.08,0:05:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切\N{\fs38}Boo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.80,0:05:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要转换话题 Rick\N{\fs38}D-don't dodge the issue, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖武器给杀手和自己动手杀人有什么两样\N{\fs38}Selling a gun to a hit man is the same as pulling the trigger!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.88,0:05:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那和什么也不做也没什么两样\N{\fs38}It's also the same as doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Krombopulos Michael想让谁死\N{\fs38}If Krombopulos Michael wants someone dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为谁能阻止他吗\N{\fs38}there's not a lot anyone can do to stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是干这一行的\N{\fs38}That's why he does it for a living.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 现在我要碾压你的"Roy"得分了\N{\fs38}Now excuse me. It's time to thrash your "Roy" Score.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你本来可以不让这种杀人的事情发生的 Rick\N{\fs38}You know, you could stop this killing from happening, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.64,0:05:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不该卖那把枪\N{\fs38}You know, you did a bad thing selling that gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.50,0:06:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你愿意 这事是可以挽回的\N{\fs38}but you could undo it if you wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯哼 这就是我跟你不同的地方了 Morty\N{\fs38}Uh-huh, yeah, that's the difference between you and me, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.66,0:06:04.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是绝不会回地毯店去的\N{\fs38}I never go back to the carpet store.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.52,0:06:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啦 这家伙要让Roy隐居山林\N{\fs38}Holy shit! This guy's taking Roy off the grid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.20,0:06:10.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的Roy连社保号都不要了\N{\fs38}This guy doesn't have a social security number for Roy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.20,0:06:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好 打扰一下\N{\fs38}Hi. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.08,0:06:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想 这里是不是有点小误会\N{\fs38}I think there was a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.60,0:06:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是个成年人 我想回家\N{\fs38}I'm an adult and would like to go home, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:23.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 当然可以 从那个管道出去就行\N{\fs38}Well, of course. Right through that tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.26,0:06:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信\N{\fs38}Unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做得很好\N{\fs38}You're doing great.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.38,0:06:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,钻根管子而已 我会的好吧\N{\fs38}I know how to crawl in a tube.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是\N{\fs38}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs38}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.60,0:06:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这比看起来要难\N{\fs38}This is harder than it looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.84,0:06:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗷\N{\fs38}Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 马可 - 波罗(类似于瞎子摸鱼的游戏)\N{\fs38}- Marco? - Polo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.86,0:06:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马可\N{\fs38}Marco?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.10,0:06:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来找我呀\N{\fs38}Come find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马可\N{\fs38}Marco?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们玩得很高兴吗\N{\fs38}You guys are enjoying this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不觉得有点被当成小孩子在哄着\N{\fs38}Don't you feel a little patronized?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.44,0:06:47.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会呢\N{\fs38}How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Jerry - Beth.\N{\fs38}- Jerry! - Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也太扯了\N{\fs38}Oh, come on. This is ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jerry 我爱你\N{\fs38}I love you, Jerry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 Beth\N{\fs38}Aw, Beth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁想看"午夜狂奔"\N{\fs38}Who wants to come watch "Midnight run"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.48,0:06:59.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带导演评论的\N{\fs38}with director's commentary on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.00,0:07:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 当然想看\N{\fs38}Yeah! Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一个来的可以调节画面设置哦\N{\fs38}First one there gets to adjust the picture setting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出厂设置里色调总是设得太高\N{\fs38}The factory tint setting is always too high!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.21,0:07:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 快让开 - 色调总是设得太高\N{\fs38}- Out of my way. - The tint setting is always too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又要去杀人啦\N{\fs38}Oh, boy. Here I go killing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您已到达Krombopulos Michael所在地\N{\fs38}You have arrived at Krombopulos Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目标位于下方\N{\fs38}Your destination is below.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.22,0:08:07.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波斯白地毯都卖完了\N{\fs38}We're all out of off-white persian.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪 我都做了什么\N{\fs38}Oh, man! W-w-what have I done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 放下武器  - 不是你想的那样\N{\fs38}- Drop the gun. - You don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个人是来杀人的\N{\fs38}This guy was gonna kill someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.14,0:08:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要杀人的就不止他一个了\N{\fs38}I guess that makes two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.16,0:08:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊\N{\fs38}Aah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么 Morty\N{\fs38}What are you doing, Morty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是星系联邦的哨站\N{\fs38}This is a galactic federation outpost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没空跟你把来龙去脉讲清楚了\N{\fs38}Look, I don't have time to tell you my entire backstory,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.38,0:08:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你外公我跟政府合不来\N{\fs38}but grandpa and government don't get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.24,0:08:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他救了我一命\N{\fs38}He saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 什么 - 啊 哦\N{\fs38}- What? - Huh?! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.34,0:08:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是Krombopulos Michael的目标吗\N{\fs38}Are you Krombopulos Michael's target?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.92,0:08:32.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你叫什么名字\N{\fs38}W-what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的种族用不上名字\N{\fs38}My kind has no use for names.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们交流的方式是你所谓"Jessica的脚"\N{\fs38}I communicate through what you call "Jessica's feet"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是"心灵感应"\N{\fs38}No, "Telepathy."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.52,0:08:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒啊 Morty\N{\fs38}Oh, good job, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你弄死了我最好的客户\N{\fs38}Y-you killed my best customer,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就救了一个会读心术的屁\N{\fs38}but you saved a mind-reading fart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:46.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屁 这个名字我喜欢\N{\fs38}I like this name fart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.16,0:08:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 你能好心拉一下\N{\fs38}Morty, would you kindly release me
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.14,0:08:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,监牢左边的控制杆 把我放出来吗\N{\fs38}by pulling that lever to the left of my cell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很痛苦\N{\fs38}I am in great pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 不要\N{\fs38}Morty, don't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38}Morty\NMorty...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 你个蠢蛋\N{\fs38}Morty, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:08:59.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 我们得赶紧带你走\N{\fs38}Oh, crap. Let's get you out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们带不走他的 他是气体\N{\fs38}We can't get him out of here. He's gaseous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.40,0:09:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他过不了传送门 Morty\N{\fs38}He's not gonna make it through a portal, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就只好都上车了\N{\fs38}Well, then, I guess we're all getting in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.04,0:09:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 对吧 呃  - 叫我屁就好\N{\fs38}- Right, uh... - fart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.46,0:09:08.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 赶紧上车\N{\fs38}No! Just j-just get in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 别这样 我想回闪电芯\N{\fs38}Morty, come on. I want to go back to Blips and Chitz.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这事儿我不想应付\N{\fs38}I don't want to deal with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 既然你态度这么明确\N{\fs38}Rick, you've been clear on the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.98,0:09:14.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想帮忙 那就走开\N{\fs38}that you don't want to help, so just go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更多人在赶来\N{\fs38}More are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.54,0:09:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,管你的 我走了\N{\fs38}Screw this. I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.31,0:09:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 快点 快点\N{\fs38}Whoa! Come on, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:27.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚出那个垃圾做的飞船 不然我们就开枪了\N{\fs38}Get out of the vehicle made of garbage or we will open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.58,0:09:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开枪\N{\fs38}Open fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠢[哔]地毯店的救屁主\N{\fs38}Stupid-ass, fart-saving, carpet-store mother[bleep]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挪开\N{\fs38}Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.90,0:09:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你[哔]的动了我调好的座位吗\N{\fs38}Wait, did you with my seat settings?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更多人要来了\N{\fs38}More are coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.42,0:09:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38}Rick\NRick!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.26,0:09:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯\N{\fs38}Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的盖尔顿转换器坏得真厉害\N{\fs38}Your geldon convertor is pretty dinged up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.18,0:10:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我孙子开飞船开得像个雄性的Obradian\N{\fs38}That's because my grandson drives like a male Obravadian.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:11.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就开地图炮了 有些所谓偏见纯属事实如此\N{\fs38}Yeah, I said it. Some stereotypes are based in fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是因为常年失修\N{\fs38}Actually, it's because of years of neglect.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的需要尊重一下这些齿轮 Rick\N{\fs38}You really need to respect your gears, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.46,0:10:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你而言 它们只是带齿的轮子\N{\fs38}To you, they're just wheels with teeth,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而在我们的文化里 是有战争\N{\fs38}but in my culture, wars have been fought...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.38,0:10:21.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听过了 你只管修好就是\N{\fs38}So I've heard. Just fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些Gromflamite应该暂时找不到我们\N{\fs38}I don't think the Gromflamites can track us now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.12,0:10:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们应该得在这待一段时间\N{\fs38}but it looks like we're gonna be here for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者 如果你拿了K. Michael掉的那把枪\N{\fs38}Or, you know, if you still have that gun K. Michael dropped,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可以直接把他的活儿给干了 然后回家\N{\fs38}we could finish the job and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.80,0:10:32.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是知道我会读心术的吧\N{\fs38}You do understand I'm telepathic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这是礼貌\N{\fs38}I'm being polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.80,0:10:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 我们得把他带回他归属的地方\N{\fs38}Rick, we're taking him back where he belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.90,0:10:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 那是哪里\N{\fs38}Oh, yeah? Where's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要去找出是谁放了这个屁吗\N{\fs38}Are you going on a quest to find he who smelt it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.18,0:10:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不小心通过一个虫洞来到这里\N{\fs38}I came here accidentally through a wormhole
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:44.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个虫洞位于 你们所谓的"滚出我的脑袋 屁\N{\fs38}located in what you call "Get out of my head, fart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.42,0:10:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你在读心 啦啦啦啦"\N{\fs38}I know you're in here. La-la-la-la "
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.60,0:10:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 它位于你们所谓的 普罗米修斯星云\N{\fs38}No, in what you call the Promethean Nebula.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 真好 只要蹦一下跳一下 再蹿个800光年就到了\N{\fs38}Oh, great. Just a hop, skip, and an 800-light-year jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rick 你想走的话 随时可以走\N{\fs38}You know, you can leave anytime you want, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.18,0:10:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你了 你这个小废逼\N{\fs38}Whatever you want to do, you little punk-ass little bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:10:58.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 Morty\N{\fs38}Thank you, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:01.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和其他的碳基生命不一样\N{\fs38}You are not like other carbon-based life-forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把其他的生命看的比自己重要\N{\fs38}You put the value of all life above your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:04.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就应该是这样\N{\fs38}It's how things should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以是这样\N{\fs38}It's how they could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.24,0:11:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全赞同\N{\fs38}I could not agree more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.64,0:11:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*四海一家*\N{\fs38}*The worlds can be one together*
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*宇宙和谐*\N{\fs38}*Cosmos without hatred*
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.26,0:11:18.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*你眼中星光亮如宝石*\N{\fs38}*Stars like diamonds in your eyes*
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*大地即是太空*\N{\fs38}*The ground can be space space space space space*
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.82,0:11:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*双足迈向平静的天穹*\N{\fs38}*with feet marching towards a peaceful sky*
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.54,0:11:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*所有的月中人都想事事如他所愿*\N{\fs38}*All the moon men want things their way*
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*但我们一定要让他们看到太阳*\N{\fs38}*But we make sure they see the sun*
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*再见吧 月中人*\N{\fs38}*Goodbye, moon men*
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:57.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*说再见吧 月中人*\N{\fs38}*You say goodbye, moon men*
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.34,0:11:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*再见*\N{\fs38}*Goodbye*
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.02,0:12:01.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再唱[哔]月球人了\N{\fs38}Shut the [bleep] up about moon men!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.80,0:12:03.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是在表演音乐剧\N{\fs38}This isn't a musical number.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在要[哔]\N{\fs38}This is a [bleep] operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静 行事低调\N{\fs38}We got to be cool and [bleep] lay low.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs38\an8}duck duck goose是儿童游戏\Nbirdie双关小鸟和高尔夫中的小鸟球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸭子 鸭子 小鸟(球)\N{\fs38}Duck, duck, birdie?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.68,0:12:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太逗了\N{\fs38}That's very funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有更逗的呢\N{\fs38}Here comes another funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 这地方太赞了\N{\fs38}Oh, this place is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都快希望能多待两天了\N{\fs38}I almost wish I could stay longer than one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.74,0:12:24.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有可能哦\N{\fs38}You just might.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:25.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥意思\N{\fs38}W-what do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是Rick和Morty再也没回来接走的Jerry\N{\fs38}These are the Jerrys whose Ricks and Mortys never came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.24,0:12:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们长住在这儿了\N{\fs38}They live here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.66,0:12:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于身份不明的人状人逃犯的离奇案件\N{\fs38}No gear-turnings as of yet in the curious case
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:53.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今仍未有进展\N{\fs38}Of these unidentified humanoid fugitives,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.04,0:12:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据报道 逃犯仍在逃于齿轮系统某处\N{\fs38}Reportedly at large somewhere within the gear system.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他妈的\N{\fs38}Son of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.88,0:12:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么那些Gromfalmite要囚禁你\N{\fs38}Why were the Gromflamites holding you prisoner?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.90,0:13:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你[哔]为什么这么重要\N{\fs38}What the [bleep] is so valuable about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.60,0:13:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不比生命更珍贵\N{\fs38}I am no more valuable than life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.24,0:13:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我能够改变原子的构成\N{\fs38}However, I am able to alter the composition of atoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:08.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像这样\N{\fs38}Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这原本是氧原子\N{\fs38}That was oxygen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.54,0:13:13.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给它加了71个质子\N{\fs38}I added 71 protons to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得了啊 这屁能拉金\N{\fs38}Terrific. The fart that pooped gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.58,0:13:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怪不得系统里的每个条子都在找我们\N{\fs38}No wonder every cop in the system is looking for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何物种只要控制了这一股屁\N{\fs38}Any species that gets ahold of this thing
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以利用它来统治银河系了\N{\fs38}Is gonna use it to take over the galaxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.56,0:13:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道这样会给我的工作带来多大的不方便吗\N{\fs38}You know how inconvenient that's gonna be to my work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:29.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人把我们卖了\N{\fs38}Somebody dropped the dime on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机头\N{\fs38}Gearhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 Rick\N{\fs38}I'm sorry, Rick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住你的赏金太高了\N{\fs38}The reward on your head is too high.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你经常说的\N{\fs38}And like you always say,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人不为己 天诛地灭\N{\fs38}You got to look out for number one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.94,0:13:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该诛的是不为老子做事的人\N{\fs38}Number one is me, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.72,0:13:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该是一伙儿的\N{\fs38}You're supposed to be my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一伙儿的 那你知道我的真名吗\N{\fs38}Friend?! Do you even know my real name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是小Revolio Clockberg\N{\fs38}It's Revolio Clockberg Junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是齿轮人中的一员\N{\fs38}I belong to an entire species of gear people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.36,0:13:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我"机头"\N{\fs38}Calling me "Gearhead"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等于管一个中国人叫"黄脸佬"\N{\fs38}Is like calling a chinese person "Asia face."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别 别扔树枝\N{\fs38}No! Not twigs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有两点 你们全都给我搞清楚\N{\fs38}Two things I want to make clear to everybody in this room
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.66,0:14:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 永远也别背叛我 二 该走了\N{\fs38}Never betray me, and it's time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许动\N{\fs38}Nobody move!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢天 那不会是\N{\fs38}Oh, my god. Are those...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:35.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 Morty 记得你说过\N{\fs38}Hey, Morty, remember when you said
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖枪和亲自扣扳机没两样吗\N{\fs38}Selling a gun was as bad as pulling the trigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你做的选择\N{\fs38}How do you feel about all these people
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在死了这么多人 你有何感想啊\N{\fs38}That are getting killed today because of your choices?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.12,0:14:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没做错 Rick\N{\fs38}I did the right thing, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这话你和机头的机蛋说去吧  - 明明是你下的手\N{\fs38}- Tell that to Gearhead's Gearsticles. - You did that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呵呵 这个时候我本来该在玩"Roy"\N{\fs38}Wrong! I'd be playing "Roy" right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.60,0:14:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 事情发展到这一步 我也别无他法\N{\fs38}At a certain point, my hands are tied, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.92,0:14:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以置信Rick能干出这种事\N{\fs38}I can't believe Rick did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 这是第八根压死骆驼的最后稻草了 - 我预下 \N{\fs38}- This is the eighth to the last straw. - Ante up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去他的\N{\fs38}You know what? Screw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱们赌点更大的吧\N{\fs38}I have a better gamble for you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.38,0:15:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咱越狱\N{\fs38}I say we escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:05.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是想走 可以从前门出去\N{\fs38}If you want to leave, you can just go out the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.68,0:15:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为我们留在这儿是被逼的吗\N{\fs38}You think we're kept here against our will?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.70,0:15:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样是违法的\N{\fs38}That would be illegal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果你们可以走的话 你们还留在这儿干嘛\N{\fs38}But if you can leave, then why are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你一样\N{\fs38}Same reason as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.32,0:15:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们是Jerry\N{\fs38}We're Jerrys.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.76,0:15:19.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要走了\N{\fs38}I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的呀 随时都可以走哟\N{\fs38}Okay, then. That was always allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 你来开\N{\fs38}Morty, take the wheel!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.32,0:15:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 哇 \N{\fs38}Whoa! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 搞什么鬼啊 Morty\N{\fs38}Geez! Damn it, Morty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁教会你开这玩意儿的\N{\fs38}Who taught you to fly this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑的 知道是我教的\N{\fs38}I'm kidding. I know that's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 Rick\N{\fs38}Um, Rick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.78,0:15:39.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈的\N{\fs38}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下看来是完蛋了\N{\fs38}Well, I guess this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 开窗\N{\fs38}Morty, crack the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.66,0:15:51.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道为什么Greg整天挑我女朋友的刺儿\N{\fs38}I wonder why Greg is always so critical of my girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.96,0:15:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 他可能就是吃醋了 想一个人占着我 \N{\fs38}Well, he'd probably like to have me to himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友之间都是这样的啦\N{\fs38}That's how friends are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.40,0:15:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是他想占着她呢\N{\fs38}Or does he want her to himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.76,0:16:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*世界可以融为一体*\N{\fs38}*The worlds can be one together*
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.40,0:16:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*宇宙本无仇恨*\N{\fs38}*Cosmos without hatred*
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.52,0:16:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*星星如你双眸中钻石般闪烁*\N{\fs38}*Stars like diamonds in your eyes*
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.30,0:16:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的人生就[哔]是个笑话\N{\fs38}My life is a [bleep] joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*再见 月中人*\N{\fs38}*Goodbye, moon men*
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.10,0:16:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*说再见吧 月中人*\N{\fs38}*You say goodbye, moon men*
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.90,0:16:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*再见 月中人*\N{\fs38}*Goodbye, moon men*
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.66,0:16:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我们出发吧\N{\fs38}All right. Let's preceed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.64,0:16:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,靠\N{\fs38}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是怪不到别人头上了\N{\fs38}Can't blame that on the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说没动静又杀得多\N{\fs38}Talk about silent but deadly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是见识过某些神经毒气\N{\fs38}I-I've seen some nerve gas,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是这团气才是够神够精啊\N{\fs38}But that this gas got nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:45.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,懂我在说啥吧\N{\fs38}You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 说够了没  - Morty 说够了我会吱一声的\N{\fs38}- Are you done? - I'll let you know, Morty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.28,0:16:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死人天上"屁-嗷"啊     \N{\fs38}Gone with the wind! Am I right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:49.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Morty 不喜欢这梗啊\N{\fs38}If you don't like that one, Morty,
